==== Dependencies ====

Java Development Kit 6 (openjdk6 and sun jdk6 tested, jdk5 should work)
Apache-Ant (tested with 1.7.1)

==== Build library with GUI as jar file ====
$ ant jar

==== Build library only as jar file ====
$ ant libjar

==== Run GUI ====
$ ant run

==== Run tests ====
$ ant test

==== Package source as Tarball ====
$ ant source